**Proposal Due Date**
1st December 2021
**Proposal Overview**
Implement derivative tokens tied to vested PSWAP strategic rewards that can be sold and traded as a liquid staking derivative

**Proposal Goals (list with explanations where possible)**
Implement a new token based on vested rewards, to be referred as VRT (Vested Reward Token) for the remainder of this proposal. 
Implement a system to transfer vesting ownership to VRT holder 
Implement an underlying system to maintain VRT value based on minter's accrued vesting rewards

**Scope of Work (describe the scope of work in as much detail as possible)**
Token and underlying stack implementation
Polkaswap UI implementation to mint tokens and marketplace implementation for trading/selling

**Current Roadblocks and Barriers to Success**
VAL vesting RFP must be completed in order to implement VRT 

**Evaluation Metrics and Criteria (definition of done should be as clear as possible)**
VRT minting/trading/ UI implementations on Polkaswap
Underlying technology merged in SORA repositories

**Submission Requirements**
Fulfill evaluation metrics and criteria.
Pull requests to paths as outlined within Submission Method done before Due Date.

**Submission Method (which folder on GitHub to submit a proposal to)**
https://github.com/sora-xor/rfps

**Project Due Date**
25 December 2021
